cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with drone localisation and trajectory planning for autonomous surface inspection. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper uses a CNN to infer projections of the skeletal model from images taken by an onboard camera. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper deals with fitting a skeletal model to images of a wind turbine. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses a non-linear least squares optimiser to simultaneously optimise both sets of parameters. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses a CNN for image inference.
